001package org.biopax.validator;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.controller.SimpleEditorMap;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.Level3Element;
005
006/**
007 * A BioPAX property cardinality and range rule.
008 *
009 * @author rodche
010 *
011 * @param <E> extends BioPAXElement
012 */
013public abstract class CardinalityAndRangeRule<E extends Level3Element> extends AbstractCardinalityAndRangeRule<E>
014{
015        public CardinalityAndRangeRule(Class<E> domain, String property,
016                        int min, int max, Class<?>... ranges) {
017                super(domain, property, min, max, ranges);
018                this.editorMap = SimpleEditorMap.L3;
019        }       
020}
